Yngve Kuilienbergs Byggn. A-B i Gbg.
translated: Kullenberg, Knut Yngve, MSc in Engineering, Director, Gothenburg, born on March 17, 1900 in Uppåkra, Malmö. First child of E. P. K. and Anna Lindholm. Married in 1934 to Maj de Vylder. Children: Kjell born in 1935, Göran in 1937, Monica and Kerstin in 1941, Uli’a-Katrina in 1944, Thomas in 1946. Completed studies in Malmö in 1919, CTI (VoV) from 1920 to 1924. Worked at A-B Skånska Gemientigj-ut. in Malmö from 1926 to 1931; served as the department head and branch manager from 1933 to 1939, and eventually became the managing director of his own company, Yngve Kullenberg's Construction Company Ltd. in Gothenburg.
